== Overview ==

A more powerful version of the [[Obliterator]], the Ravager hits enemies so hard it even drains their reactors.
== Where to Acquire ==
The Ravager superweapon can be acquired from the vault of [[TRAFs]] in the [[Talsian Warfront]], as well as purchased from the market in the [[North West Quadrant]] of [[Gamma]].
